### Add a Pirate Chain View Key
# Associates a Pirate Chain viewing key with the authenticated user's account.
# This allows the system to monitor incoming transactions for this user.
# The system will attempt to import the key into the Pirate Chain node.
# @name addViewKey
POST {{host}}/api/payments/piratechain/addresses/view-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viewKey": "zxview..."
}

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# (No response body)


